    "body": "### Description\n\nHi, \n\nIt appears that https://github.com/neovim/nvim-lspconfig/blob/master/lsp/erlangls.lua configures a server that is unmaintained:\n\nhttps://github.com/erlang-ls/erlang_ls/issues/1596\n\nand explicitly deprecated in favor of\n\nhttps://github.com/whatsapp/erlang-language-platform\n\nSo I would suggest that be moved over as the default. Will try to get to this myself but making an issue for tracking and to ask the question about how this should be / usually is handled as I'm sure it's happened before. Thanks.",
